PRESCIMONE v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [P. C. No. 15,

September Term, 1958.]

Decided June 9, 1959.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

PER Curiam.

Petitioner’s application for leave to appeal under the Post *652Conviction Procedure Act is denied for the reasons set out by the court below.

Application denied.
